# Local-dev build-context trim for the backend image (context root = csharp/).
# Excludes build artifacts and frontend deps that the Dockerfile restores/builds
# inside the container, so `docker build` does not stream hundreds of MB over the
# WSL 9p mount. Does not affect image correctness.
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/out/
**/coverage/
**/TestResults/
typesense-data/
**/*.user
.git/
